Invocation Name: baby names
des:
To invoke the Baby names skill, say "Alexa, open baby names". 
First, tell Alexa if you have a preference for a gender or not. Then Alexa will suggest one random name, to keep listening to suggestions just say "one more".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
